	dprr:hasNoteText "Sent by Decimus Brutus in Cisalpine Gaul with despatches to the Senate (Cic. Fam. 11.18.1, cf. 12.1; perhaps the senator L. Volumnius named in Varro RR 2.4.11, and Cic. Fam. 7.32.1)." .
